rows.label: tev040801_MSG0001
rows.name:
I love your Earth-alien strategy books.
I want to read them all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0002
rows.name: But when your ship crashed, much data was lost.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0003
rows.name: And when you did find data, Goetia destroyed it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0004
rows.name:
I hope you find the rest before Ganglion does.
It would be great loss otherwise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0009
rows.name:
Your Earth library data is fascinating.
I read it every day![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0010
rows.name:
Sun Tzu... Jomini... Clausewitz...
Earth produced many fine tacticians.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0011
rows.name:
I thought 10,000 suns of war had taught Prone all
there was to know. But I was fool.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0012
rows.name:
I wish to be like Napoleon.
Lead army to victory with sage strategy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0013
rows.name:
...Please come see me again, Earth alien.
I have matter to discuss with your kind.
But first I must catch up on tactical studies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0018
rows.name: Do you not admire their Napoleonic tactics?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0019
rows.name:
They attacked with full force in wedge formation.
Forced you to congregate in large group.
But this was just ruse![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0020
rows.name:
Meanwhile, Wrothians stood by. Quickly moved in for
surprise attack on restricted hangar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0021
rows.name:
I thought Ganglion were only violent rabble.
I was wrong. They are formidable foes.
We must ready strong counter-tactics![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0026
rows.name:
BLADE must not face Ganglion's force head-on.
You do not have chance of winning.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0027
rows.name:
You must think strategically. Use gifted warriors.
Deal crippling blows to key Ganglion military elements
one by one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0028
rows.name:
Ganglion is composed of many disparate groups.
If you do this, you might break army.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0029
rows.name: I think your team can accomplish this![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0030
rows.name:
Use your smarts! Deploy your tactics!
Prove they are no match for you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0035
rows.name:
Is it like other Lifehold wreckage? Does this "core" hide
secret knowledge brought from Earth?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0036
rows.name: If so, I may have to work up courage to visit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0037
rows.name:
For I must read every Earth-alien strategy writing!
Ha ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG0038
rows.name: ...But first, you must give permission to enter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG1001
rows.name:
[ST:playername ], thank you for proving
worth of my tactics.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG1002
rows.name:
Now I have Vio's respect. We can work together as
fellow tacticians and destroy enemy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG1003
rows.name:
Soon they will call me "Mira's Sun Tzu"!
Just wait! You will see![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG2001
rows.name: Vio will not stop rubbing victory in my face...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG2002
rows.name: He thinks this proves him right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG2003
rows.name:
Mine were sounder tactics. Not his. Hmph!
Next time, I will gather more enemy intelligence.
Use trusted soldiers to enact their demise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040801_MSG2004
rows.name: Then I will surpass Napoleon himself![ST:wait ]
